<head>
    <title>Slick Playground</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link href="~/css/slick.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="~/css/Index_Slider.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">

</head>

<body>
    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <!-- Content Header (Page header) -->
        <div class="content-header">
            <div class="row">

                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <!-- Widget: user widget style 1 -->
                    <div class="card card-widget widget-user">
                        <!-- Add the bg color to the header using any of the bg-* classes -->
                        <div class="widget-user-header bg-info">
                            <h3 class="widget-user-username">Alexander Pierce</h3>
                            <h5 class="widget-user-desc">企劃部</h5>
                        </div>
                        <div class="widget-user-image">
                            <img class="img-circle elevation-2" src="/theme/dist/img/user1-128x128.jpg" alt="User Avatar">
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-footer">
                            <h5 class="description-header">恭喜本月壽星，別忘了給你的工作夥伴一個祝福~</h5>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- /.widget-user -->
                </div>
                <!-- /.col -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card card-widget widget-user">
                        <!-- Add the bg color to the header using any of the bg-* classes -->
                        <div class="widget-user-header bg-blue">
                            <h3 class="widget-user-username">Mary Huang</h3>
                            <h5 class="widget-user-desc">總務部</h5>
                        </div>
                        <div class="widget-user-image">
                            <img class="img-circle elevation-2" src="/theme/dist/img/user4-128x128.jpg" alt="User Avatar">
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-footer">
                            <h5 class="description-header">本周即將到職同仁，請各部門多協助關照~</h5>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- /.col -->
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card card-widget widget-user">
                        <!-- Add the bg color to the header using any of the bg-* classes -->
                        <div class="widget-user-header bg-blue">
                            <h3 class="widget-user-username">Mary Huang</h3>
                            <h5 class="widget-user-desc">業務部</h5>
                        </div>
                        <div class="widget-user-image">
                            <img class="img-circle elevation-2" src="/theme/dist/img/user5-128x128.jpg" alt="User Avatar">
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-footer">
                            <h5 class="description-header">本周即將到職同仁，請各部門多協助關照~</h5>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="for_slick_slider autoplay">
                <div class="item">
                    <img src="~/images/slides_images/78f9e76820ddce34ba0e5b8ea151a7094b990f7f.jpeg" />
                    <div class="overlay"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <img src="~/images/slides_images/employee.jpg" />
                    <div class="overlay"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <img src="~/images/slides_images/employee_recognition-908535308-5c5b362a46e0fb0001587318.jpg" />
                    <div class="overlay"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <img src="~/images/slides_images/Employee-Experience.png" />
                    <div class="overlay"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <img src="~/images/slides_images/employee-incentive-travel.jpg" />
                    <div class="overlay"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <img src="~/images/slides_images/The-Divide_6x4.jpg" />
                    <div class="overlay"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <img src="~/images/slides_images/unnamed.jpg" />
                    <div class="overlay"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="container-fluid">

                <div class="row mb-2">
                    @*<h1>佈告欄</h1>*@
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Main content -->
            <section class="content">

                <!-- Default box -->
                <div class="card-red">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3 class="card-title">資安公告</h3>

                        <div class="card-tools">
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-tool" data-card-widget="collapse" title="Collapse">
                                <i class="fas fa-minus"></i>
                            </button>
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-tool" data-card-widget="remove" title="Remove">
                                <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        1.使用資訊設備請注意資訊安全，請勿點擊不明信件或網址。<br />
                        2.公司資訊請勿任意攜出或者傳輸至儲存設備、雲端服務。<br />
                        3.有任何資安疑慮或問題請洽 IT 人員。<br />
                    </div>
                    <!-- /.card-body -->
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        IT 部門
                    </div>
                    <!-- /.card-footer-->
                </div>
                <!-- /.card -->
                <!-- Default box -->
                <div class="card-blue">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3 class="card-title">疫情公告</h3>

                        <div class="card-tools">
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-tool" data-card-widget="collapse" title="Collapse">
                                <i class="fas fa-minus"></i>
                            </button>
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-tool" data-card-widget="remove" title="Remove">
                                <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        1.因應疫情升溫，上班期間請全程配戴口罩。<br />
                        2.如有疑似 Covid-19 症狀，請就醫診查並通知主管及HR，待狀況排除後再進公司上班。<br />
                        3.有任何疑慮或問題請洽 HR 人員。<br />
                    </div>
                    <!-- /.card-body -->
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        HR 部門
                    </div>
                    <!-- /.card-footer-->
                </div>
                <!-- /.card -->
                @*@Html.ActionLink("編輯", "BulletInList", new { }, new { @class = "btn  btn-primary btn-lg", style = "filter: grayscale(50%)" })*@

            </section>
                <!-- /.content -->
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- /.content-wrapper -->
        <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.2.0.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
        <script src="~/js/slick.min.js"></script>
        <script src="~/MyJs/Index_Slider.js"></script>
</body>